{"tid":237602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人知到西藏政教合一封建落後既農奴制度","createTime":"2017-05-10T13:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T13:17:15.000Z","uid":98232,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04eb35cb327a702a86a6259ca4847e2966cc483d","tid":237602,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R96607c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR96607c.jpg&h=543bc6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg&h=1b31e584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西藏比人既感覺係自由 寧靜 <br />\n宗教文化氣息濃厚既地方<br />\n但其實西藏係1950年以前都係一個<br />\n由政教合一農奴制度既封建社會所組成<br />\n西藏身份地位主要有貴族 僧侶  農奴<br />\n係西藏貴族擁有西藏80%既土地<br />\n不同地區都有不同領主所支配<br />\n所以一般人擁有自己既土地<br />\n作耕種都係唔可能既事<br />\n農奴一出生就要交不同既稅比貴族領主<br />\n甚至去做僧侶都要交稅<br />\n咁苛刻既稅收一般人係無法負擔<br />\n只好向貴族領主賣身一身為奴"},{"pid":"f8ef84990ae5a1056acfdb6ef987094ca3ab74a4","tid":237602,"uid":64347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:09:44.000Z","msg":"而家咪好囉得一個貴族<br />\n<br />\n共產黨"},{"pid":"1e2ee341f75a3dddf3b9cb72f798cef056d9dbeb","tid":237602,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家咪好囉得一個貴族<br />\n<br />\n共產黨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗯"},{"pid":"41fd93c64d6c0622c4fa43fa408f183572be5523","tid":237602,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:13:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R96607c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR96607c.jpg&h=543bc6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg&h=1b31e584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西藏比人既感覺係自由 寧靜 <br />\n宗教文化氣息濃厚既地方<br />\n但其實西藏係1950年以前都係一個<br />\n由政教合一農奴制度既封建社會所組成<br />\n西藏身份地位主要有貴族 僧侶  農奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係西藏貴族擁有西藏80%既土地<br />\n不同地區都有不同領主所支配<br />\n所以一般人擁有自己既土地<br />\n作耕種都係唔可能既事<br />\n農奴一出生就要交不同既稅比貴族領主<br />\n甚至去做僧侶都要交稅<br />\n咁苛刻既稅收一般人係無法負擔<br />\n只好向貴族領主賣身一身為奴</blockquote><br />\n同香港差唔多"},{"pid":"5897af05795ec4d2ddbe839de3397152aa2e6dc2","tid":237602,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:17:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R96607c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR96607c.jpg&h=543bc6ef&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/10/204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F10%2F204753_c2a3b8b0e714f948e8f0923d8906b87b.jpg&h=1b31e584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西藏比人既感覺係自由 寧靜 <br />\n宗教文化氣息濃厚既地方<br />\n但其實西藏係1950年以前都係一個<br />\n由政教合一農奴制度既封建社會所組成<br />\n西藏身份地位主要有貴族 僧侶  農奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係西藏貴族擁有西藏80%既土地<br />\n不同地區都有不同領主所支配<br />\n所以一般人擁有自己既土地<br />\n作耕種都係唔可能既事<br />\n農奴一出生就要交不同既稅比貴族領主<br />\n甚至去做僧侶都要交稅<br />\n咁苛刻既稅收一般人係無法負擔<br />\n只好向貴族領主賣身一身為奴</blockquote><br />\n同香港差唔多</blockquote><br />\n其實真係差唔多<br />\n差在舊西藏領主貴族會拎農奴練槍法同斬手"}]}